// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2026-0025 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: 65e92488-41cc-55c9-9396-861f98699deb

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:12.04*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:14.04*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:15.04*")
